class_notes: For midwifery students only. Online with synchronous sessions: Zoom. On-campus dates: TBD.
course_description: Students will gain the skills to effectively promote and support breastfeeding and human lactation in a variety of settings.  Consideration will be given to how culture, ethnicity, and socioeconomic status influence a woman's decision to breastfeed.  Legal and ethical issues will also be addressed.
